{"tid":2386216,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港澳辦及中聯辦批評夏博義挑戰一國兩制底線","createTime":"2021-01-29T12:30:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:28:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f87538597059646a42b776865ab3382c2a3b252f","tid":2386216,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:30:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】港澳辦及中聯辦發聲明批評大律師公會。新主席夏博義表示，游說政府修改港區國安法是挑戰一國兩制底線。<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦指，夏博義剛上任便質疑全國人大常委會權威，要特區政府修改國安法，政治用心一目了然，大律師公會已偏離了專業團體應有的行為規範，任何組織不應心存幻想，以為挑戰一國兩制原則可以不受懲罰。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦亦批評夏博義濫用大師公會主席身分，在基本事實和法律原則上誤導公眾，公然踐踏法治原則。公會在過去三年在政治化的道路上越行越遠，中聯辦絕不允許有團體披着「專業」外衣亂港禍港，必須堅定維護香港憲制秩序，堅決執行港區國安法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422237&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH7Hzcpgs3fvoPbc8izSauP4%3D&h=f6fbd481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D422237&h=dde5ceb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=422237</a>"},{"pid":"9827d6433b81d5708f8a61879b31952b4bd67832","tid":2386216,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"大律師就是極權的幫兇"},{"pid":"51695a96bf7229d3ad6d5054c360cf94041bdc92","tid":2386216,"uid":241399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:33:43.000Z","msg":"全個中國都係由外行人講法律"},{"pid":"d8bd281bcd61c55a1e7377810b90026ee5e1b953","tid":2386216,"uid":108016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:34:33.000Z","msg":"如果用国安法拉咗佢就好睇"},{"pid":"616ab47b493879f42a6af5354ffa71447872d32f","tid":2386216,"uid":76804,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9827d6433b81d5708f8a61879b31952b4bd67832","tid":2386216,"uid":177168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T12:31:52.000Z","msg":"大律師就是極權的幫兇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20